sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/BasketballPlayer> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthDate> ?date ; <http://dbpedia.org/property/highlights> ?h FILTER regex(?h, "MVP") } ORDER BY DESC(?date) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 4

sparql2nl.en: Can you name four of the most recent basketball players who have been recognized as "MVP" (Most Valuable Player) at some point in their career?
sparql2nl.original_en: Who are the four youngest MVP basketball players?
